1.	Install Node.js v4.4.7 from https://nodejs.org/en/download/releases/

2.  Install Visual Studio Community Edition from https://www.visualstudio.com/downloads/

2.	The python 2.7 and Win64OpenSSL-1_0_1m are available in the following box file https://paypal.box.com/s/ggd99xt0rttzgdx9vsye095gac3vt9p6

3.	Win64OpenSSL-1_0_1m.exe has to be installed .Please install It in C:\OpenSSL-Win64

4.	Also set path to C:\OpenSSL-Win64;C:\OpenSSL-Win64\bin;C:\OpenSSL-Win64\include

5.	For some machines it is asking for directory name openssl (it did not asked in my machine)

6.	Finally run npm install bignum in command prompt make sure it runs without any errors
